OS-Adobe_CS2_KeyGen_Tryout_to_Full.exe u open  this file you enter the serial number at the beginning of the installation and then you wait until the program is installed.
Then as for the activation you open the program ->options->activation by phone ->enter the request code(activation number) and then an answer code(authorization code) is being produced you enter it and all is over.
During the steps you have to choose indesign Cs2 4.0
Youre done!
